Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.18,0:00:08.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,转送代码
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.31,0:00:10.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要传送了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.42,0:00:11.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸 把手给我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.91,0:00:19.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.24,0:00:21.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.69,0:00:23.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结衣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.02,0:00:25.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.19,0:00:26.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.56,0:00:28.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像没有地图情报呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.06,0:00:30.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道亚丝娜在哪里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.02,0:00:31.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.97,0:00:35.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常… 离这里非常的近
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.13,0:00:38.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,往这边
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.55,0:01:10.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是… 世界树的顶端
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.61,0:01:16.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,空中都市什么的 根本就没有不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.32,0:01:21.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么终极任务啊 这不全都是骗人的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.42,0:01:22.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可原谅
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.86,0:01:29.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对啊 等救出亚丝娜之后再说其它这些
